data.description: Here's your opportunity for a contemporary home with quality construction and meticulous attention to detail and design. Boasting a fully loaded interior with an inviting entertainment room complete with equipment and a captivating stone fireplace, this home is a unique gem. With over 2000 square feet of contemporary living space, it features an open floor plan ideal for modern living. The main level primary suite has a coffered ceiling and includes an updated full bath. The stone fireplace takes center stage in the main living area, seamlessly connecting to the dining area and Kitchen with Corian counters, updated appliances, and a pantry, making it perfect for gatherings and entertaining. The lower level is a haven for entertainment with its media area and recreation room, accompanied by a full bedroom and full bath. On the upper level, you'll find two more bedrooms and another full Bath, providing plenty of space for family and guests. Outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the deck and the large lot with mature trees, offering a peaceful outdoor escape. This property is also part of a community with fantastic amenities, including a pool.
